Cell C announced that it has doubled the amount of data received by its MediaPlay TopUp and Postpaid customers for Black Friday. From 23 November, customers who sign up for a 24-month MediaPlay contract will receive double data which lasts the full length of their contract. This deal will be available until 6 January 2019 from Cell C outlets as well as the company’s call centre and online portal. “We decided to not only limit this fantastic offer to Black Friday but to extend it into the new year,” said Cell C Chief Commercial Officer Junaid Munshi. “We welcome the opportunity to offer the best data deals for our customers.” Below are the MediaPlay TopUp and Contract deals with double data.